										----------- VI EDITOR ---------
										
										
										
										
										
										
										
										
										
										
										

ESC  - comand mode

I - insert mode

X - delete symbol 

dd - delete line

dw - delete word

:wq  - save

:q!  - no save 

SHIFT + O  space between line

Y - copy line

P - paste 


/ - search  n - nextone


:set number   - line number show 

:0 - first line 
:4 4th line 






